  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5829878/" class="title-link">很自我的文字</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5829878"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/70514763/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u70514763-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/70514763/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">公子泠然</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-04-01"
      class="main-meta">2013-04-01 22:35:12</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5829878_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  本以为这么薄薄的一本书很快就能读完，结果事实证明我大错特错。里面有对词的考究与鉴赏，有对瓷器与古画的研究。后来查了一下作者，才知道原来是致力于考古及文学研究的才女……  总觉得这样一本书写的很是自我，并非是给想浅浅的了解一下便罢了的人读的。我看书总是喜欢看前...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
